text: Falsamblesthis ibiyara is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Marinoni in 1978. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Falsamblesthis ibiyara. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1978
